_:N79a8860aaf5442b4ab13bdc3b8a9de50 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Prior to becoming General Counsel at Sellafield Ltd, Ian was in-house counsel to the British Nuclear Fuels group, including Sellafield Ltd, Magnox, Westinghouse and Uranium Asset Management from 2000 until joining the law firm DLA as a partner in 2006, moving to King and Wood Mallesons in 2015 and Squire Patton Boggs in 2017.</p>\n\n<p>Ian had been involved in advising on and drafting procurement and commercial contracts, with a particular specialism in the nuclear sector.</p>\n\n<p>He also has extensive experience in large scale projects in the construction, IT, plant and equipment and service delivery sectors.</p>\n\n" .
